## Key Decisions

### Workspace Structure
- Root folders: `brand/`, `website/`, `documents/`, `ops/`
- Numbered prefixes avoided — descriptive folder names are clearer
- Each folder has a README so any team member can navigate without asking

### Website Architecture
- Next.js 16, App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4
- shadcn/ui for components, Framer Motion for animations
- Modular: each page section is a standalone module in `modules/`
- `"use client"` only where needed (hero for motion, nav for state)
- Build verified clean: static prerender, 0 errors

### Documents
- All documents in Markdown — portable, no tool dependency
- Invoice numbering convention: SH-YYYY-NNN (e.g. SH-2026-001)
- Company profile covers: who we are, what we do, TaoLink, Landlord HQ

